column5: The son and G/F have been fishing 3 days straight. I came home today to see what I had been missing out on.LOL  Boys a chip of the ol block.LOL
hmmm....chip off the OLD block, Pike, Walleye, Perch, New Years,...I think I know where they are fishing! LOL
see, you should be out there fishing too you can't work all the time  oh and looks like they did well
Awesome Brian.... I'd sure love to get out for some of that there kinda ice fishing...  Happy New Year to you all....
Well get out the B.  Aren't you feeling sick, cough, cough  Nice fish for sure.  Joey
Excellent fish!!!  Ya see Brian, there's other fish in the water besides those danged ol' Green Trout and Tiny Moothed Bass!
Nice fish Ryan got there you should get out bro i will be out next Saturday you want to go and i do know where he is lol  rob
What's this chip off the old block crap... I've never seen you with that many fish !  Looked like a good day out for them.
i have two lakes in mind here... shes either small or has wings.
Smart   ,sssssssssssssssssssss Go    or something will,ya,s.  I got to get this scanner of mine up and running. I,ll show youzzzzzzzzzzz.
Now Brian.. keep your darn body parts away from the scanner ........
Wayne, I almost sprayed my monitor with the water I was drinking!
